---
title: Steak and Shrimp au Poivre with Bacon Caesar Salad and Fries
description: On the menu tonight is a premium steakhouse classic that is sure to warm the soul! Juicy steak is adorned with umami-filled pepper sauce and paired with succulent shrimp, creamy Caesar salad and oven fries.
